list.name: DROP-THE-BASS
list.description: Janet deploys a speaker that deals x damage per second to all enemies in the area until it gets destroyed.

list.name: BACKSTAGE-PASS
list.description: Janet's next High Note pushes her back, even over walls. The more focused her attack is, the further she'll be pushed back.
